Diablo® II: Resurrected™  is a remastered version of Diablo® II, the heralded action-RPG. Pursue the mysterious Dark Wanderer and vanquish the demonic hordes of the Burning Hells as you uncover the fate of the Prime Evils Diablo, Mephisto, and Baal.

Enjoy all five acts from Diablo II, including the Lord of Destruction expansion, as you return to the flowing jungles of Kurast, the craggy stronghold of Harrogath, the arid desert of Lut Gholein, and more in up to Ultra HD 4K resolution. 

To take a sneak peek at this revived classic, preregister for a chance to partake in an upcoming Diablo II: Resurrected PC Technical Alpha and prepare to face death head on!

